Authorisation
The following products are authorised for the purposes of Articles 4(2) and 16(2) of Regulation (EC) No 1829/2003, in accordance with the conditions set out in this Decision:
(a) foods and food ingredients containing, consisting of, or produced from MON-ØØØ21-9 maize;
(b) feed containing, consisting of, or produced from MON-ØØØ21-9 maize;
(c) products, other than food and feed, containing or consisting of MON-ØØØ21-9 maize for the same uses as any other maize with the exception of cultivation.
